  <brief_title>The Impact of Surgical Treatment of Endometriomas on Ovarian Reserve</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Surgical Treatment of Ovarian Endometriomas on Ovarian Reserve: a Randomised Controlled Trial of Laparoscopic Ovarian Cystectomy Versus Cyst Ablation - a Pilot Study</official_title>
